## Proxy rules
ProxyRequests Off

ProxyPass /images/ !
<Location /images/>
  ProxyPassReverse !
</Location>

ProxyPass /api/ ajp://localhost:<%= @api_port %>/api/
<Location /api/>
  ProxyPassReverse ajp://localhost:<%= @api_port %>/api/
</Location>

ProxyPass / ajp://localhost:<%= @data_port %>/
<Location />
  ProxyPassReverse ajp://localhost:<%= @data_port %>/
</Location>
